# Sentinel — Agentic PR Review Guide

## 0. Before you start

Read (or re-read) the canonical docs for the phase covered by this PR:

| Doc | Purpose |
|-----|---------|
| `AGENTS.md` | Non-negotiable rules — **any violation is a blocker** |
| `PLAN.md` | Product strategy & AI hero path |
| `ROADMAP.md` | Per-phase tasks, What/Goal/Test, DoD |
| `SPEC.md` | Guardrail parameters, contract interfaces, LLM schema |
| `UI.md` | Frontend token system, themes, a11y |

Find the relevant ROADMAP task(s) stated in the PR title/body. Verify that the PR
covers **exactly** those tasks — no more, no less.

---

## 1. How to build and test locally

```bash
# 1. Install JS/TS deps
pnpm install

# 2. TypeScript checks
pnpm -r typecheck        # must exit 0
pnpm -r lint             # must exit 0
pnpm -r test             # must exit 0
pnpm -r build            # must exit 0

# 3. Solidity — offline (no RPC needed)
forge build --root contracts --offline          # must exit 0
forge test --root contracts --no-match-contract ForkTest -vv   # all pass

# 4. Solidity — fork tests (requires Mantle RPC in .env)
forge test --root contracts --fork-url $MANTLE_RPC_URL \
  --match-contract ForkTest -vv

# 5. Validate Docker compose stack
docker compose config
```

> **solc binary:** if `forge build` can't fetch solc from binaries.soliditylang.org,
> install it manually — see README §"Note for Claude Code on the web".

